      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "『ⅢX　新たなる挑戦　#6』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.1199999723,
      "endTime": 2.6133332729000003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "さて。このシリーズでは、ⅢXの三人がそれぞれ\n未経験のことに挑戦する様子を、お届けしています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.4333330313,
      "endTime": 11.2005891005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.4005889098
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "先日とうとうkanaが、アメリカの大学入試の\n共通テストを、受けに行きまして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.4005889098,
      "endTime": 17.8625843207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "今日この後、結果がオンラインで確認出来るそうです\nkana、これ何点くらい取れていればいいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.049251159,
      "endTime": 25.5912464937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.7845797698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……目標の大学には\n合計で1400点以上あれば、手が届くって感じかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.7845797698,
      "endTime": 33.601949517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.7952828884
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "kana凄い頑張ったし、大丈夫だと思うんだけど\nやっぱ、ちょっとだけ不安かな～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.7952828884,
      "endTime": 40.834421014899995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……それじゃ、行くわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.0344211102,
      "endTime": 45.362788629600004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.0344211102
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.562788725
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "kanaの、今回の試験の点数は――\nえーと、896点……だいたい900点ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.562788725,
      "endTime": 56.2939448834,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3007.2112750000033
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ！？　……え、本当に！？\nちょっと待って、自己採点よりだいぶ低いんだけど！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4872782548,
      "endTime": 63.6980944475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.4872782548
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "あ！？　もしかして回答欄ズレてた！？\nそんな～、kana、あんなに勉強頑張ったのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.904761076,
      "endTime": 72.6847606182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.904761076
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.8714271705
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "貴方が頑張っていたのは、私達もよく知っているわ\n参考書も英語の辞書も、書き込みばかりだったもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.8714271705,
      "endTime": 81.53142682720001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.7247601033
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "でもまずは、試験お疲れさま会をしましょう\nあんな自信満々だったのに、残念だったわね……ぷっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.7247601033,
      "endTime": 91.1595896245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "そうよね。英語は得意だからって言ってたのに\nまさかケアレスミスなんて……ぷくくっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.3662564438,
      "endTime": 99.6130590599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.3662564438
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "……テ、テメェら、覚えてろよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.8197256884,
      "endTime": 104.5721974215,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.8197256884
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――11月23日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.5788640501,
      "endTime": 106.5788640501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "『突撃！　fran・朝のルーティンの真実とは！？』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.5788640501,
      "endTime": 108.3296356203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.3296356203
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁ……ああ、まだ眠いわ\n朝早くから呼びだして、一体、何をするつもりなの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.1788386188,
      "endTime": 119.8684756121,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.0618089837
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "franのやつ、『パリコレモデルの朝のルーティン』\nとかいう、クッソつまんない動画出してきたじゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.0618089837,
      "endTime": 126.9446661158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.157999182
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。ヨーグルトとナッツを食べて、ヨガをやっていた\n何一つ学びのない映像だったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.157999182,
      "endTime": 134.707999182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.9079992774
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "でしょ。だから、朝から家に押し掛けてやって\nあいつの本当の朝の姿を、ファンにお届けしようって訳",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.9079992774,
      "endTime": 143.86799912479998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "それってただのドッキリじゃないかしら\n……まぁ、いいわ。私も付き合うわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.0613324009,
      "endTime": 150.7965025744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.0613324009
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.9965024791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "私の車を、センスがないだのと散々馬鹿にしてくれて\nあっちも少しは、笑い物になってもらわないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.9965024791,
      "endTime": 158.03094709730001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "あいつ、kanaの残念会なんだから～とか言いながら\n居酒屋で寝落ちして、結局kanaが面倒見たし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.2309469066,
      "endTime": 166.7836000285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.2309469066
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_03-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……あの残念会も、一応撮ってはおいたけど\nさすがにあの映像は、永久に封印するしかないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.9702667715,
      "endTime": 176.102194071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.9702667715
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
